 the Hub.</p>|14:        </div>|8:        |30:        <div class="metadata">|55:            <p><strong>Skill Name:</strong> hf-jobs</p>|97:            <p><strong>Main Documentation:</strong> <a href="jobs/SKILL.md">jobs/SKILL.md</a></p>|81:            <p><strong>Scripts Directory:</strong> <code>jobs/scripts/</code></p>|87:            <p><strong>References Directory:</strong> <code>jobs/references/</code></p>|14:        </div>|8:        |29:        <div class="section">|29:            <h2>Overview</h2>|248:            <p>This skill focuses on running real workloads via Hugging Face Jobs. It includes ready-to-run UV scripts and guides for authentication (HF tokens), secrets vs env vars, timeouts, hardware selection, and pushing results to the Hub.</p>|14:        </div>|0:|29:        <div class="section">|39:            <h2>Core Documentation</h2>|34:            <ul class="file-list">|20:                <li>|56:                    <a href="jobs/SKILL.md">SKILL.md</a>|62:                    <div class="file-path">jobs/SKILL.md</div>|180:                    <div class="file-description">Complete skill documentation (how to submit jobs, tokens/secrets, timeouts, persistence, and how to use the bundled scripts)</div>|21:                </li>|17:            </ul>|14:        </div>|0:|29:        <div class="section">|31:            <h2>References</h2>|34:            <ul class="file-list">|20:                <li>|79:                    <a href="jobs/references/token_usage.md">token_usage.md</a>|79:                    <div class="file-path">jobs/references/token_usage.md</div>|151:                    <div class="file-description">Token best practices: secrets vs env, permissions, common errors (401/403), and secure patterns</div>|21:                </li>|20:                <li>|77:                    <a href="jobs/references/hub_saving.md">hub_saving.md</a>|78:                    <div class="file-path">jobs/references/hub_saving.md</div>|144:                    <div class="file-description">How to persist results: push datasets/models/files to the Hub (ephemeral job filesystem)</div>|21:                </li>|20:                <li>|85:                    <a href="jobs/references/hardware_guide.md">hardware_guide.md</a>|82:                    <div class="file-path">jobs/references/hardware_guide.md</div>|107:                    <div class="file-description">Flavor selection guidance for CPU/GPU/TPU workloads</div>|21:                </li>|20:                <li>|87:                    <a href="jobs/references/troubleshooting.md">troubleshooting.md</a>|83:                    <div class="file-path">jobs/references/troubleshooting.md</div>|122:                    <div class="file-description">Common failure modes (timeouts, missing deps, OOM, auth) and fixes</div>|21:                </li>|17:            </ul>|14:        </div>|0:|29:        <div class="section">|28:            <h2>Scripts</h2>|34:            <ul class="file-list">|20:                <li>|90:                    <a href="jobs/scripts/generate-responses.py">generate-responses.py</a>|83:                    <div class="file-path">jobs/scripts/generate-responses.py</div>|163:                    <div class="file-description">vLLM batch generation: load prompts/messages from a dataset, generate responses, push dataset + card to Hub</div>|21:                </li>|20:                <li>|88:                    <a href="jobs/scripts/cot-self-instruct.py">cot-self-instruct.py</a>|82:                    <div class="file-path">jobs/scripts/cot-self-instruct.py</div>|167:                    <div class="file-description">CoT Self-Instruct synthetic data generation (reasoning/instruction) + optional filtering, pushes dataset + card</div>|21:                </li>|20:                <li>|82:                    <a href="jobs/scripts/finepdfs-stats.py">finepdfs-stats.py</a>|79:                    <div class="file-path">jobs/scripts/finepdfs-stats.py</div>|163:                    <div class="fil